review: I had health issue so went to hospital. Doctor explained to me very well. We had been in last month of July 2020. I am satisfied with the treatment given. I can recommend doctor to my family or friends. Medicine was prescribed by the doctor. Scanning, blood test was also done. Doctor gave some suggestions, because of COVID we didn't take treatment. Doctor told diet plan only when we asked her. There was no waiting time in the hospital, it was for 10 minutes only. Hospitality was good. Doctor was friendly and explained well.

I had consulted the doctor and it was for health concern. ****** *** **** ** ******** *** It was for gynecology related issue. She spoke very clearly. I am satisfied with the treatment given. I can recommend doctor to my family or friends. * ******* ** **** ********* **** *** ******** ********* * *** ******* ***** ** ***** ****** I was there in hospital for 10 days, later covid issue came. So I didn't visit the doctor. I can recommend doctor to my family or friends. Scanning was also done. Everything was good. Medicine was prescribed by the doctor for one month. Even thyroid tests was done. There was less waiting time in the hospital, it was for 30- 40 minutes. Doctor told us to take healthy food, vitamin D tablets was suggested and juices. I am good now. Hospitality was good.

the consultation was for myself it was for a pregnancy concern the doctor is wonderful gave a right treatment I am very much satisfied with the consultation everything went fine with the doctor actually due to far distance had to change the doctor I would surely recommend the doctor to others

I had met the doctor and it was for gynaecology related. Consultation was fine by the doctor. I am satisfied with the explanation given by the doctor. Tests were prescribed. There was  waiting time in the hospital when we went. It was for 30 -60 minutes. I am visiting hospital since last 10 years.

I had been to hospital and it was for gynaecology related. Consultation was fine by the doctor. I am satisfied with the explanation given by the doctor. Medicine was prescribed by doctor during consultation. Tests were done. There was less waiting time in the hospital. I had been to hospital and it was for POCOD issue. The doctor was good in treating me. I had 2 sessions. Waiting time was less. She told to take medical tests. Medicines was prescribed by the doctor. I am satisfied with the treatment given. I can recommend doctor to my family or friends. I was able to recover based on treatment. Hospitality was good. Doctor told to take healthy diet.
